              <div class="section-title">
                <div>
                  <h3>Planner notes</h3>
                  <p>Reasonable defaults baked into the engine.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="notes" id="defaultsNote"></div>
            </article>
            <article class="insight-card">
              <div class="section-title">
                <div>
                  <h3>Scenario flags</h3>
                  <p>Watch the widow’s trap, IRMAA jumps, and forced RMD acceleration.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div id="warningChips"></div>
              <div class="callout" id="strategyCallout"></div>
            </article>
          </div>

          <article class="insight-card">
            <div class="section-title">
              <div>
                <h3>State-specific takeaways</h3>
                <p>Best-effort heuristics, not a substitute for tax prep or a CFP / CPA review.</p>
              </div>
